## SEO turns content into a growth system.

A good article still needs a reason to exist. SEO research shows what people are trying to solve, how they phrase it and what information they need before taking action.

When content and SEO work together, every page has a job: educate, compare, convert or support authority.

## Where teams often go wrong

Publishing one-off posts without internal links, measurement or search intent often creates a library nobody uses. A stronger system connects topics, page roles and business outcomes.
